The easiest way to get live exchange rates of over 170 currencies and over 100 cryptocurrencies for free right on your smartphone or tablet.

Our cryptocurrency converter application is a an easy and elegant tool. You can convert over 170 currencies and over 100 cryptocurrencies for free on your device! You can easily search for the currency you want. We automatically update all of our exchange rates every minute to keep you up to date with the latest changes in all currencies.


✓ We have a very easy to use interface, so anyone can use it simply without having to watch any tutorial. We've worked hard to make it easy for you.
✓ Start using our multicurrency converter without creating an account, then download it now and start using it in seconds.
✓ The best thing is that our easy currency converter is FREE and it will stay free for life. So there are no hidden costs, no special membership and no annual subscription.
✓ We will keep you updated with the latest exchange rates for over 170 currencies and over 100 cryptocurrencies. So even if you are a crypto investor, you can still track the price of Bitcoin and many other cryptocurrencies for free.

MAIN FEATURES :

- cryptocurrency conversion
- Free and live exchange rates
- Real time market
- Multi-currency display
- More than 170 currencies
- Over 100+ CryptoCurrencies
-  Favourite pairs of conversion
- A simple and intuitive design
